import React from 'react' import { Stack } from 'react-bootstrap' import './css/contactITEM.css' import {format} from 'date-fns' const ContactITEM = ({icon ,name, lastestMSG ,dateTime}) => { const e = format(new Date(dateTime) , "dd-MM-yyyy"); return (
{name}
{lastestMSG}
{e.toString()}
 ) } export default ContactITEM
